      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"feeling seen\" thing... it feels so out of reach though. Everyone else is so connected, and I'm just out here in this tiny apartment in a country where I'm just a stranger. If I stopped showing up to work or stopped answering my phone, it would probably take weeks for anyone to even notice. It’s like I’m already gone, just waiting for the rest of the world to catch up.",
